WeatherApp built the Weather App as a free app. This SERVICE is provided by VISHWA IN GT at no cost and is intended for use as is.

This page is used to inform visitors regarding our policies with the collection, use, and disclosure of personal information if anyone decided to use our Service.

Information Collection and Use

The Weather App does not collect or store any personal information. The app may request access to your location in order to provide accurate weather information for your area. Location data is used only for showing weather updates and is not stored, shared, or sold.

Permissions

Location Access: Used only to fetch local weather data.

No other sensitive permissions are required or collected.


Data Sharing

We do not share or sell any information with third parties.

Security

We value your trust in providing us your information, thus we are striving to use commercially acceptable means of protecting it. But remember that no method of transmission over the internet is 100% secure.

Changes to This Privacy Policy

We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. Thus, you are advised to review this page periodically for any changes.

Contact Us

